<p>When a <b><tt>summary</tt></b> is given.  Red when required, green when
optional. Hint: move over input.</p>

<div>
  <label for="animal" class="form-label">favorit animal</label>
  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="animal"
      aria-describedby="animal-descr" required />
  <div id="animal-descr" class="form-text">
    Specify the endangered spieces you want to support.
  </div>
  <div class="change change-new" for="animal"
      data-changed-in="20251010" data-summary="add pet">
    Your favorit animal will get an extra meal.
  </div>
</div>
